{"tid":1815294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[帶返風向] 義士感謝祭","createTime":"2020-01-07T11:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T15:36:19.000Z","uid":6891,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2aea423b5628639eabac72503f04ca27ad4042db","tid":1815294,"uid":6891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:53:38.000Z","msg":"首先 大家唔好再捉鬼了<br />\n由今日起 我地要養成好習慣<br />\n同埋唔好比人亂帶風向了<br />\n<br />\n係遊行期間見到裝修緊<br />\n無論你覺得係佢真義士定係狗都好<br />\n請大家一齊大嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">辛苦晒義士 核彈都唔割<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n可以的話 可以行埋去幫手舉遮<br />\n仲記唔記得 點解6月之後會有black bloc?<br />\n原先就係想做cover<br />\n等真正做野既人可以被cover以降低風險<br />\n<br />\n唔好因為濫捕而驚<br />\n真係魔法師同被濫捕既人<br />\n其實被咬後既待遇係好唔同的<br />\n雖然你被濫捕後 受到待遇同警暴已經好過份<br />\n但真義士可能面對既係 真送中 被消失 etc<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果落場做緊野係自己人<br />\n佢會覺得被認同<br />\n而無比大家割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n久而久之 班狗扮既<br />\n見到佢地就算扮得太明顯<br />\n我地都要多謝佢地<br />\n只要大家一齊真心多謝佢地幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地自然會無癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣真義士又落場做少左野<br />\n被捕既可能性又低左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f7b65f3039f745502ff4af2add201199ad9b03","tid":1815294,"uid":6891,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:01:01.000Z","msg":"推呀 成個連登 係度亙割做乜鳩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪比人帶風向 我地一齊做感謝祭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝返各小隊過去大半年既努力<br />\n無佢地 69 612 71果陣已經收晒皮<br />\n<br />\n拖左咁耐 人地有灰心都好正常<br />\n但唔好中班5毛計<br />\n真義士唔會亂咁表明身份的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0e9a6df69b9d2f472920bbe8d94c19c0477659","tid":1815294,"uid":36984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:01:34.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"300ef2eaa2da7c89bda13e561d2e4c05bff500f5","tid":1815294,"uid":106851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:01:47.000Z","msg":"辛苦晒咁多位"},{"pid":"19840da44827fb57f351037fde2e77975d1afb56","tid":1815294,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65edb0b02d04ba722a5e518e7e7dffb738318e3f","tid":1815294,"uid":69334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:02:34.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割唔只係口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港獨立   唯一出路</span></strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新症正名：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>中國肺炎</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c816a71a58067dee604e605935aef2c546bab1","tid":1815294,"uid":6891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:03:58.000Z","msg":"大家跟住我一齊講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該晒義士 多謝你為香港付出</span></span>"},{"pid":"30b071794be837b98f70a7e084a001c4b565e215","tid":1815294,"uid":189417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:07:04.000Z","msg":"借力打力"},{"pid":"cca48b6c3336c9321303a7d9f2296366235640a7","tid":1815294,"uid":6891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:07:05.000Z","msg":"大家口遁d狗果陣就叻<br />\n依加叫你地用 口遁多謝返自己人<br />\n咁簡單 無成本點解唔做?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多謝義士</span></span>"},{"pid":"04b218fa96a98c56fb67f1a2f8efc1535322e4c5","tid":1815294,"uid":59472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:07:39.000Z","msg":"辛苦晒你"},{"pid":"44c6f6600d38a7ee0b111661b02c21513156e7ca","tid":1815294,"uid":342419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:08:26.000Z","msg":"辛苦晒義士 核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"eec87631aced7fc5097f2cc64d13605a0caa92a1","tid":1815294,"uid":234540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:08:59.000Z","msg":"Support"},{"pid":"1c9ca10a4d01d1d6baa3551d45e0c4a32fe96660","tid":1815294,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc7d0ed2590a73682e0d7ad25abd891b14b1981","tid":1815294,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:09:44.000Z","msg":"【借位，與主題無關】<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n試下用<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「沒有普選，唯有獨立」</span></strong>做口號<br />\n<br />\n牌面上你係爭取緊無人有異議既雙普選。實質上你提供緊清晰既路徑，解釋緊點解要獨立、以及為獨立提供正當性。<br />\n<br />\n對於和理非，一開始可以則重係「雙普選」上面。但潛移默化地灌輸佢地獨立既可行性。對於獨派，亦解決左「時機」問題；因為嚴格上口號並唔係直接提倡獨立，但同時宣傳緊獨立。"},{"pid":"dcc4e712b2daa23db430f653aa74add941b72ff5","tid":1815294,"uid":329448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:10:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/c-7dcVw0VUY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fc-7dcVw0VUY&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=2984e548\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/c-7dcVw0VUY</a>"},{"pid":"ae16a227c7eaca80b9350bac7730ac4a8f82272e","tid":1815294,"uid":6891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:13:14.000Z","msg":"義士佢地裝修緊 整緊魔法果陣<br />\n佢地其實都唔知自己做緊既野<br />\n有無市民意授權<br />\n如果大家好似14年咁樣同d勇武割鳩晒<br />\n咁佢地就會無人support佢地<br />\n呢樣野就係正正中共想做野<br />\n<br />\n所以好簡單 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一句支持 一句唔該晒</span></span><br />\n大家要養成良好習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951a09ac99ee48b872078effc7b23e545ffcac72","tid":1815294,"uid":282316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:20:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a2a0def2c6adaf4a21ba3ef9cf337ef023277ea","tid":1815294,"uid":6891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:33:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真義士 多謝晒你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n狗扮既 都唔該晒你地</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf514601a38172ba0f3fe9b5fafe6d4dc623b2c","tid":1815294,"uid":261995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:44:12.000Z","msg":"辛苦晒義士 核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"9d990b7da7239c61f6e8ff78b1791e14e8a45d40","tid":1815294,"uid":321231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:00:16.000Z","msg":"多謝義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2159ac7c9de82887c8a773a22b7c1888c402697a","tid":1815294,"uid":6891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:23:27.000Z","msg":"多謝義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2995cf940cb83e1780ce64c22a4989df1a1c19eb","tid":1815294,"uid":4931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:31:09.000Z","msg":"每日全黑，如果黑仔俾狗拉咗最多48小時。<br />\n<br />\n反正9拉。"},{"pid":"e8e9937a39977548a90736af0c66da285a8bb1aa","tid":1815294,"uid":39492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:32:32.000Z","msg":"多謝所有有參與過呢場運動嘅義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不分和勇，全部多謝<br />\n希望大家一齊行落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e5d18aa9ba15bb5544f5890a20841adea1e3d40","tid":1815294,"uid":78686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:32:59.000Z","msg":"與其係到開po<br />\n不如下次發夢見到人捉鬼 好似藍絲咁一律私了先有用"},{"pid":"30f7e970ac9a67d557c6c38618b743fcb81d8699","tid":1815294,"uid":137716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:33:33.000Z","msg":"多謝義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}